我18岁时，站在党旗下宣誓入党，我对这片土地有着深深的热爱。
When I was 18, I was sworn in under the Party banner and I had a deep love for this land.
平时我不爱拍照，连新闻报道中用的图片都是自己临时拍的，但等这场“战疫”打赢了，等我们的祖国好起来，我想好好和家人吃顿团圆饭，拍张全家福。
Usually I don't like to take pictures, even the pictures used in news reports are taken by themselves, but when the "plague" win, when our motherland is better, I want to have a good dinner with the family, take a picture of the whole family.
口述 | 罗　皓整理 | 吴　雪我是罗皓，今年44岁，是一名退伍军人，2019年3月，我从湖北省咸宁市崇阳县调配到崇阳县下属的天城镇，成为了一名四级主任科员。
I am Lo Hao, 44, a veteran. In March 2019, I was transferred from Chongyang County, Xianning City, Hubei Province, to the Tin Town subordinate to Chongyang County, becoming a Grade 4 director.
2月4日，我突然登上了新闻头条，传播最广的那篇文章《这位湖北干部，火线提拔》刷屏，让大家开始认识我。
February 4, I suddenly appeared in the headlines, the most widely spread article "Hubei cadre, fire promotion" screen, let everyone start to know me.
网友对我褒奖有嘉说“能者上劣者下”，一天之内我接了十几通记者的采访电话，同事们都纷纷调侃我成为了“网红”。
I have been praised by the netizens to praise the "ability above the inferior", a day I received a dozen reporters telephone interview, colleagues have ridiculed me as "net red.
其实在我看来，自己并没有做什么突出的事情，天城镇里和我一样奋斗在一线的人很多，我也从来没想过自己会被嘉奖。
In fact, in my opinion, I did not do anything outstanding, the days and towns and I like the struggle in the line of many people, I never thought I would be praised.
罗皓在运送病人的金杯车里　受访者供图记得1月20日，疫情开始有了苗头，我们天城镇党委书记廖旦发布通知，要组织干部紧急开会，全面部署防控工作方案。
With the outbreak beginning to take hold on January 20, Liao Dan, the secretary of the party committee of our town, issued a notice to organize an emergency meeting of cadres to work out a comprehensive prevention and control programme.
我虽然来这里工作时间不长，但从小生长于此，天城镇——崇阳县最大的镇、防疫阻击战的主阵地，这两点基本的判断还是错不了的。
Although I came here to work for a short time, but I grew up here, the day-town - Chongyang County's largest town, the main anti-epidemic battle position, these two basic judgments can not be wrong.
据我了解，天城镇下辖28个村,11个社区，农业人口5.3万人，城镇人囗13万人，距离武汉市中心车程仅一个小时。
As far as I know, under the jurisdiction of the days and cities 28 villages, 11 communities, 53,000 agricultural population, 130,000 urban population, Wuhan city center only one hour away from the car.
镇上前往咸宁周边城市，特别是武汉打工、上班、做生意的人特别多，粗略估算，20万总人口中，流动人口接近有上万人。
There are particularly large numbers of people working, working and doing business in the cities around Xiangning, especially Wuhan, where, according to rough estimates, the floating population is close to tens of thousands of people out of a total population of 200,000.
从初一开始，就是返乡敏感期，对我们的挑战很大，但也没有任何一个人畏惧过。
From the beginning of junior high school, is a sensitive period to return home, to our great challenge, but no one has ever been afraid.
当时我接到崇阳县颐和医院消息，说人员配备不够，需要多一辆车来运送确诊和疑似病例以及密切接触者，因为以前在部队开过车，我觉得自己完全能胜任这个工作，就主动报了名。
I received word from the Summer Palace Hospital in Chongyang County that I was understaffed and needed an additional vehicle to transport confirmed and suspected cases, as well as close contacts, since I had been driving in the army before and felt fully qualified for the job, so I volunteered for the job.
至于害不害怕，会不会感染，我根本没有多余的心思去纠结和担心什么。
As for the harm is not afraid, can infect, I have no extra thoughts to worry about what.
当时镇上条件有限，没有很正规的用车，但征用的这辆车也算接近，有点类似救护车的7座金杯面包车。
Conditions in the town were limited and there was no regular use of cars, but the car was close enough to the seven gold-cup vans that resembled ambulances.
在出发之前，我会把车用酒精、84消毒液里里外外消毒一遍，穿好防护服，戴好护目镜、手套和口罩，当时和我一同去的“战友”，社区1个人，村里1个人，镇上干部1个人（就是我），一般是3个人。
Before I set out, I would disinfect the car alcohol, disinfectant 84 inside and outside, put on protective clothing, goggles, gloves, and masks, then go with me "comrade-in-arms," a man from the community, a man from the village, a town cadre (who is me), generally three people.
如果工作不好做，就会增派两个人。
If the work is not done well, two more will be added.
镇上干部正在为村民测体温　图 |天城镇政府官网第一次转送病人，我们就遇到了阻力，前后做工作用了三个小时。
Township officials were taking a temperature test at RTS & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45;
在镇上有着100多户的中型小区，有一栋住户陈燕（化名）老公确认为新冠肺炎，陈燕和21岁、13岁的两个孩子，作为第2类密切接触者，需要隔离观察。
In a small, medium-sized town with more than 100 families, Chen Yan, a resident (not her real name), was identified by her husband as New Crown Pneumonia, while Chen Yan and her 21-year-old two children, aged 21 and 13, were in close contact with Category 2 and required isolated observation.
陈燕当时很不愿意配合，在她看来，隔离在家也一样能做，不一定非要到医院去。
Chen Yan was very reluctant to cooperate, in her view, isolation at home can do the same, do not necessarily have to go to the hospital.
最重要的是陈燕也害怕周边邻居会另眼看待，心理上有些接受不了。
The most important thing is Chen Yan is also afraid of neighbors will look at the other side, some psychological unacceptable.
我清楚镇上的风俗，特别能理解陈燕的顾虑，和我同去的镇干部，主要做心理疏导，我们就劝她要往大方向想，以及告诉她在家隔离存在的风险。
I knew the customs of the town, especially to understand Chen Yan's concerns. The town cadres I went with were mainly engaged in psychological counseling, and we advised her to think big and tell her about the risks of segregation at home.
三个小时我们一行五人真的像居委会大妈一样苦口婆心地劝，终于把对方劝了下来。
Three hours we a group of five people really like a neighborhood committee mother like painstaking advice, finally persuaded the other side down.
相比之下，老人的工作可能更难做一些。
Older people's jobs, by contrast, may be harder to do.
有一位60多岁的刘姓住户，他妻子已经确诊，他属于疑似病例，已经有点咳嗽了，但他却说“死在房里都不去医院”。
A 60-year-old resident named Liu, whose wife has been diagnosed as a suspect, has coughed a bit, but says he "died in his room not to go to the hospital."
后来社区书记、镇书记都派专人来劝解，跟他讲事情的严重性，来来回回，上午两三个小时，下午两三个小时，晚上他又说要吃完晚饭再说。
Then the secretary of the community, the clerk of the town, sent a messenger to tell him the seriousness of the matter, and came and went, two or three hours in the morning, two or three hours in the afternoon, and in the evening he said he would finish his dinner.
我们就守在他家门口等着他出来，后来被我们磨得没办法，才同意跟我们走。
We waited in front of his house and waited for him to come out, but then we had no choice but to go with us.
后来，事实证明这种坚持是对的，老人目前已经确诊，幸好当时早点来医院，否则有可能更危险，因为他本身还有高血糖、高血压等病症。
Later, it turned out to be true. The old man was now diagnosed, but fortunately he had come to the hospital earlier or he might have been more dangerous because of his own high blood sugar and high blood pressure.
天城镇部署防疫工作　图 |天城镇政府官网当然，大部分人都是很配合的，镇上一位老人，因在与武汉亲戚有过拜年接触后感染。
AT THE TIANNIUM STOCK DEPLOYMENT AT RATE & # 45; Of course, most people do. An old man in the town got infected after visiting relatives in Wuhan on New Year's Eve.
当时家里还带着一个10岁的孙子，在房间里没有直接接触。
The family was also carrying a 10-year-old grandson, who had no direct contact in the room.
我去接老人入院隔离，男孩就很懂事，像个男子汉一样对爷爷说了安慰的话：“爷爷你去吧，我会照顾好自己。
I went to the hospital to pick up the elderly isolation, the boy is very sensible, like a man said to Grandpa comfort: "Grandpa, you go, I will take care of themselves.
”当时我一个大男人站在旁边，眼泪就下来了。
"I stood next to a big man and tears came down.
我是1月28日运送了一批11人，后面几天又运送了好几次，前后护送30余人到颐和医院进行集中观察。
I delivered a group of 11 people on 28 January and several more in the following days, escorting more than 30 people to the Summer Palace Hospital for intensive observation.
工作强度的确不小，每天早上6点出门，连续一周凌晨两三点休息，每天工作除了护送病人，我还会不定时地运送社会各界捐助的物资，比如体温计、口罩、酒精、矿泉水、宣传画等，反正随叫随到。
The intensity of the work is not small, every morning at 6 a.m., two or three in the morning in a row, daily work in addition to escort patients, I will also occasionally transport donated materials from various sectors of society, such as thermometers, masks, alcohol, mineral water, posters, etc., on demand.
要说不累是假的，但我觉得自己军人出身，一定能撑得下去。
It's not true to say you're not tired, but I think I'm a soldier and I'm sure I can survive.
我一天与隔离人员接触20多个小时，忙的时候，就吃点泡面充饥；开车时间长，颈椎和腰也会酸痛；最尴尬的是不敢上厕所，防护服本来就紧缺，我们能把损耗降到最低就降到最低，留给一线的医护人员。
I spend more than 20 hours a day in contact with isolated people. When I am busy, I eat noodles to stay my hunger. I drive long hours and my spine and waist ache. The most embarrassing thing is not to go to the toilet.
罗皓正在运送病人　图 |咸宁日报罗皓在搬运物资　图 |澎湃新闻视频因为经常接触确诊人员的关系，镇里专门安排了值班室供我们住宿，大概二十几平方米的房间，可以放两张单人床、一张桌子和一台电视机，我和市场部的一位干部住在一起，他是劝说员，我是司机，忙完一天回来，我俩常常聊天，我想在这个特殊时期，换成任何一个人都愿意做出一些牺牲。
Lo Hao is carrying a patient at Ro Hao Daily. Because of frequent contact with confirmed staff, a duty room has been set up in the town for us. About 20 square metres can accommodate two single beds, a table and a television.
2月5日我11点钟到宿舍，算是比较早的一天，同事帮我打了饭，放在微波炉里热好了，有菜有肉，这么多天，第一次能吃上一口应时的热饭，觉得很幸福。
February 5 I arrived at the dormitory at 11 o'clock, is an early day, my colleagues helped me to cook, put in the microwave hot, vegetables and meat, so many days, the first time to eat a hot meal, feel very happy.
从1月28日开始，我一直没回家吃过一次饭，年三十晚上只在家待了半个小时就走了。
I haven't been home for a meal since Jan. 28, and I've only been at home for half an hour on the evening of January 30.
我有一儿一女，妻子也无条件地支持我。
I have a son and a daughter, and my wife supports me unconditionally.
现在，太想太想和家人在一起吃一顿团圆饭了。
Now, too eager to have a reunion dinner with the family.
罗皓去年9月，带女儿和儿子来上海游玩　受访者供图2月5日，我接到了县委通报嘉奖，并提拔为镇党委委员，你问我对自己的评价，我想说，对于嘉奖，受之有愧。
I received a letter of commendation from the county councilor and promoted to the township Party committee. You asked me what I think of myself and I should like to say that I feel guilty about the award.
我只是镇上抗疫工作中一个非常普通的小角色，我也只是做了自己应该做的分内工作，真的不必宣传报道。
I'm just a very ordinary little part of the town's fight against plague, and I'm just doing what I'm supposed to do. I really don't have to advertise.
身边像我这样的人真的太多了，大家都在奉献，可能领导觉得，我是直接接触、运送确诊和疑似病人，有一定胆识。
There are too many people like me around, we are all dedicated, the leaders may feel that I am direct contact, transport diagnosis and suspected patients, have a certain amount of courage.
但能得到这份荣誉，绝对不是我一个人的功劳，而是全体一线同事们的嘉奖。
But can obtain this honor, definitely is not my own credit, but all frontline colleagues' commendations.
在这场抗疫阻击战中，我们很多干部都是无所畏惧地冲在第一线的，党委副书记徐干本来身体不太好，在分管后勤保障时，亲自搬方便面，烧开水，扛医疗用品，背消毒桶，每天只睡三四个小时。
Xu Gan, deputy secretary of the Party committee, who was not in good health, carried instant noodles, boiled water, carried medical supplies and carried disinfectant buckets for only three or four hours a day when he was in charge of logistics.
天城镇部署防疫工作　图 |天城镇政府官网31岁的镇党委组织委员陈祯和我一样，也是在一线运送病人的干部。
Chen Zhen, a 31-year-old member of the township government's official network, is the same cadre that I used to transport patients on the front line.
疫情一出，他就主动请缨上一线，父母从老家来看他，也没打上照面，连换洗衣服都是妻子送到镇政府门卫室。
His parents had come to see him from his home village and had not even been exposed. His wife had sent him to the township government gate for washing.
我18岁时，站在党旗下宣誓入党，我对这片土地有着深深的热爱。
When I was 18, I was sworn in under the Party banner and I had a deep love for this land.
平时我不爱拍照，连新闻报道中用的图片都是自己临时拍的，但等这场“战疫”打赢了，等我们的祖国好起来，我想好好和家人吃顿团圆饭，拍张全家福。
Usually I don't like to take pictures, even the pictures used in news reports are taken by themselves, but when the "plague" win, when our motherland is better, I want to have a good dinner with the family, take a picture of the whole family.
征集令《新民周刊》现面向全国征集新冠肺炎采访对象和真实故事：如果你是参与抗击新冠肺炎疫情的医护人员或其家属，我们希望聆听你的“战疫”故事，也希望传达你的诉求。
Call for orders The New People's Weekly is now soliciting interviews and true stories from all over the country: If you are a healthcare worker or family member involved in the fight against the outbreak, we hope to hear your "epidemic" story and convey your message.
如果你是确诊、疑似患者本人或家属，我们希望了解你和家人如何“抗疫”的过程，让外界了解你的真实经历。
If you are a confirmed, suspected patient or family member, we would like to know how you and your family have responded to the epidemic and let the outside world know about your true experience.
如果你是疫情严重地区的普通市民，我们希望展现你的乐观，并倾听你所需的帮助。
If you are an ordinary citizen of a highly affected area, we hope to show your optimism and listen to the help you need.
如果你是公共服务人员或各类捐助者，我们希望看到你的“最美逆行”，记录下你的无私。
If you are a public service provider or a variety of donors, we want to see your "most beautiful retrograde" and record your selflessness.
……抗击新冠肺炎疫情，我们诚征对疫情了解的社会各界人士，提供相关线索，说出你的故事，让我们用新闻留存这一切。
To fight the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic, we sincerely invite all sectors of the community to understand the epidemic, provide relevant clues, tell your story, let us use the news to retain all this.
